OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening with some
OL,7,Fprolonged spells of late evening
OL,8,Fsunshine. Remaining dry overnight with
OL,9,Fclear spells. Mostly light winds, a
OL,10,Ftouch breezier near the coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FDry and warm with lengthy
OL,13,Fsunny spells for much of the day, but
OL,14,Fsunshine turning somewhat hazier as
OL,15,Fcloud spreads south in the afternoon
OL,16,Fand evening. Warmer in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
